# Markdown File Creation Policy

**NEVER create `.md`, `.txt`, or other documentation files unless the user explicitly asks for them.**

This includes:
- README.md files
- Documentation files (*.md)
- Any other markdown files

## Exception

it is okay to update project_schema.yaml proactively. 

Only create `.md` files when the user explicitly requests:
- "Create a README"
- "Add a CONTRIBUTING.md file"
- "Make a documentation file"
- Or any other direct request for markdown files
